-- MOVES-Commercial Bank of Qatar says appoints Macdonald as deputy CEO
-- By Matt Smith
-- Mon Dec 08, 2014 06:21AM EST
-- None



DUBAI, Dec 8 (Reuters) - Commercial Bank of Qatar <COMB.QA> (CBQ), the Gulf Arab state's second-largest lender by assets, has appointed Colin Macdonald as deputy chief executive, the company said on Monday.

Macdonald has been an advisor to CBQ's chief executive since February, according to his LinkedIn profile.